		<description>
			<p>A yklwa (pronounced YICK-ul-wah) is a simple melee weapon that is the traditional weapon of Chultan warriors. A yklwa consists of a 3-foot wooden shaft with a steel or stone blade up to 18 inches long. Although it has the thrown weapon property, the yklwa is not well balanced for throwing.</p>
		</description>
		<setters>
			<set name="category">Weapons</set>
			<set name="cost" currency="gp">1</set>
			<set name="weight" lb="3">3 lb.</set>
			<set name="slot">onehand</set>
			<set name="range">20/60</set>
			<set name="damage" type="piercing">1d8</set>
			<set name="proficiency">ID_WOTC_TOA_WEAPON_PROFICIENCY_YKLWA</set>
		</setters>
	</element>
	
